Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.00,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.09,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎样的天气 I need you!!
